Package projektarbeit.immobilienverwaltung.model

Class Mieter

java.lang.Object
projektarbeit.immobilienverwaltung.model.Mieter
@Entity public class Mieter extends Object
Represents a tenant entity with details about the tenant and their rental agreement. This entity is mapped to the database table 'mieter'.

      public Mieter(String name, String vorname, String telefonnummer, double einkommen, LocalDate mietbeginn, LocalDate mietende, double kaution, int anzahlBewohner)
      Constructs a new Mieter (tenant) with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      name - Last name of the tenant.
      vorname - First name of the tenant.
      telefonnummer - Contact number of the tenant.
      einkommen - Monthly income of the tenant.
      mietbeginn - The start date of the tenancy.
      mietende - The end date of the tenancy.
      kaution - Deposit amount paid by the tenant.
      anzahlBewohner - Number of inhabitants living in the rented property.
